    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2 col-sm-2 col-md-2"></div>
        <div class="col-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4" style="line-height: 1em;">
            <h4 class="text-white">About</h4>
            <p.not() class="text-muted" style="font-size:11px;">I am a major comuter enthusiast. I love everything from programming to security to networking to hardware. I have been using
            computers since I can remember, and have always been interested in how they work. I pride myself in being diverse in my skillset, I know
