            it has been a long time. I hope you enjoy my crappy ruby on rails website.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-2 col-sm-2 col-md-2"></div>
        <div class="col-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
            <h4 class="text-white">Contact</h4>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="https://github.com/PwndDepot/" class="text-white">Checkout my Github</a></li>
                <li class="text-white">Email: travis@brunimail.com</li>
                <li class="text-white">Discord: PwnDepot#2355</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-dark">
<a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Trav's Portofolio Site</a>


<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarsDefault">
<ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
    <li class="nav-item active">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/" style="font-size:18px;">Home</a>
    </li>
        <% if !user_signed_in? %>
                <li class="nav-item" style="font-size:18px;">
                    <%= link_to 'Sign In' , new_user_session_path, class: "nav-link" %>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item" style="font-size:18px;">
                    <%= link_to 'Sign Up' , new_user_registration_path, class: "nav-link" %>
                </li>
            <% else %>
            <li class="nav-item" style="font-size:18px;">
                <%= link_to 'New Project', new_project_path, class: "nav-link" %>
            </li>
        <% end %>
</ul>


    <div class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark box-shadow">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
            <button class="d-none d-md-block navbar-toggler" href="#collapse1" type="button"
                data-target="#navbarToggleExternalContent" data-toggle="collapse" aria-controls="navbarHeader"
                aria-expanded="true" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <li class="nav-item navbar-nav" style="font-size:18px;">
        <%= link_to 'My Account', edit_user_registration_path, class: "nav-link", style: "color:white;" %>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item navbar-nav" style="font-size:18px;">
        <%= link_to('Sign Out', destroy_user_session_path, class: "nav-link" , method: :delete) %>
    </li>
    <% end %>
</div>
</nav>


<% if flash[:notice] or flash[:alert] %>
<br>
<center>
<p id="notice"><b><%= notice %></b></p>
<p class="alert"><b><%= alert %></b></p>
</center>
<% end %>

<div class="jumbotron" style="background-color:lightgrey;margin-bottom:5%;padding-bottom:0px">
<div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-3">Welcome!</h1>
    <p>Thanks for checking out my site! Here users can post their projects to show off to the world! </p>
</div>
</div>
<br>
<center><h2>Projects</h2></center>
<br>
<br>
<div class="container">
<div class="row text-left">
<% @projects.each do |project| %>
    <div class="col-md-4" style="border: 1px solid black;">
        <h2><%= project.name %></h2>
        <p><%= project.description %></p>
        <p><%= link_to 'Show', project, class: ["btn", "btn-secondary"], :style => "color: white;" %></p>
    </div>
<% end %>
</div>
</div>